Lavv, or, a discourse thereof in foure bookes. Written in French by Sir Henrie Finch Knight, his Maiesties Serieant at Law. And done into English by the same author. Nomotechnia. English Finch, Henry, Sir, d. 1625. I. L., 17th cent.
[8], 496, 499-506, [16] p.
Printed [by Adam Islip] for the Societie of Stationers, London : 1627.
A translation of "Nomotechnia", but a different version of the text first published in Law French in 1613. Editor's introduction signed: I.L. Printer's name from STC. Includes index. The first leaf and the last leaf are blank. Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
